      "content": "The Furniture API is a software interface that allows developers to access and integrate information about furniture products and designs into their applications. It provides product listings with filtering, product detail lookup by SKU, stock management, featured product flags, and discount application across an inventory of furniture items.\n\nContact Support:\n Name: Furniture API",
